---
layout: base.njk
title: Partner With Us - Full Supply
description: Become a People Investor
pageCss: true
---
{% from "components/macros.njk" import button, section, sectionHead, hero, ctaBand %}

{% set paypalUrl = "https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=6SL49EHP9KB9S&source=url" %}

{# ===================== HERO ===================== #}
{% call hero(
  "Become a <span class='pwu-hero__accent'>People </span>Investor",
  subtitle="Be a <b>Part</b> of <b>Something Bigger</b>",
  bgImage=("/assets/img/partner-hero.jpg" | url),
  overlay="light"
) %}
  {{ button("Donate", paypalUrl, attrs='target="_blank" rel="noopener"') }}
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== OUR PHILOSOPHY (green band) ===================== #}
<section class="section pwu-band-green">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2 class="pwu-band-green__title">Our Philosophy</h2>
    <p>We believe giving is a ministry to God and others. Therefore we will not urge or pressure someone to give. Rather, we believe people should give freely and graciously. Therefore, we are committed to what is right in the eyes of God and man by fulfilling the Lord&rsquo;s work in a proper, ethical and honest manner.</p>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===================== TOGETHER WE SHAPE ETERNITY ===================== #}
{% call section(narrow=true) %}
  <div class="pwu-center">
    <h2>Together We Shape Eternity</h2>
    <p>Your generosity combined with our cause equals greater kingdom impact. Let&rsquo;s face it, money is an essential resource that allows us to do what we do best worldwide.</p>
  </div>
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== PARTNERSHIP DIFFERENCE ===================== #}
{% call section(tone="alt", narrow=true) %}
  <div class="pwu-center">
    <h2>How will your partnership make a difference?</h2>
  </div>
  <h3 class="pwu-results-head">It results in:</h3>
  <ul class="pwu-checklist">
    <li>Opportunities to mentor and reach women toward maturity in Christ</li>
    <li>Mentors who invest in others today and for future generations</li>
    <li>Exemplary leaders who volunteer in their local church, communities and non-profit organizations.</li>
    <li>Missionaries who serve Christ in other parts of the world</li>
    <li>Professional business women advance their careers or becoming business owners</li>
  </ul>
  <blockquote class="pwu-quote">
    <p>&ldquo;Each man should give what he has decided in his heart to give, not reluctantly or under compulsion, for God loves a cheerful giver.&rdquo;</p>
    <p class="pwu-quote__cite">~ 2 Corinthians 9:7</p>
  </blockquote>
{% endcall %}

{# ===================== INVESTOR BENEFITS (soft green band) ===================== #}
<section class="section pwu-band-soft">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pwu-benefits">
      <div class="pwu-benefits__body">
        <h2>Our Team of Investors Benefit by:</h2>
        <ul class="pwu-checklist pwu-checklist--soft">
          <li>The personal satisfaction that your contribution helps train leaders and change lives in the U.S. and abroad.</li>
          <li>Extended invitations to attend or participate in special events.</li>
          <li>Knowing your contributions to Full Supply are tax-deductible under Section 501(c)(3).</li>
          <li>Receiving updates on the impact your donations are having, such as newsletters, personal handwritten notes and periodic telephone calls to pray for you.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="pwu-benefits__media">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/img/partner-connie-band.jpg' | url }}" alt="" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===================== FAQ ACCORDION ===================== #}
<section class="section pwu-band-soft pwu-faq-band">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
  <div class="pwu-center">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="pwu-faq" data-pwu-faq>
    <div class="pwu-faq__item">
      <h3 class="pwu-faq__heading">
        <button class="pwu-faq__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pwu-faq-1" id="pwu-faq-1-btn">
          <span>How will my donation be spent?</span>
          <span class="pwu-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div class="pwu-faq__panel" id="pwu-faq-1" role="region" aria-labelledby="pwu-faq-1-btn" hidden>
        <p>At Full Supply, we are firmly committed to good stewardship to the funds entrusted to us by our friends and investors given to us transforms a woman&rsquo;s life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pwu-faq__item">
      <h3 class="pwu-faq__heading">
        <button class="pwu-faq__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pwu-faq-2" id="pwu-faq-2-btn">
          <span>Can I afford to make a donation?</span>
          <span class="pwu-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div class="pwu-faq__panel" id="pwu-faq-2" role="region" aria-labelledby="pwu-faq-2-btn" hidden>
        <p>Only you know if you are able to afford to give. However, donations can be as low as $1.00; on the other hand, the sky&rsquo;s the limit! Full Supply stands by our belief that one should give cheerfully from the heart.</p>
        <p>Full Supply mentees are unable to afford the full cost of the Full Supply Mentoring Program. In order to keep the Mentoring Program accessible and to ensure the stability for the ministry, Full Supply invites ongoing support (annually, quarterly or monthly) from faithful partners who will invest in our current and future Christian leaders.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pwu-faq__item">
      <h3 class="pwu-faq__heading">
        <button class="pwu-faq__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="pwu-faq-3" id="pwu-faq-3-btn">
          <span>Can my donation to go a specific campaign?</span>
          <span class="pwu-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div class="pwu-faq__panel" id="pwu-faq-3" role="region" aria-labelledby="pwu-faq-3-btn" hidden>
        <p>Yes. The investor has the ability to designate a contribution to a specific program/campaign.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===================== TESTIMONIAL QUOTE (green band) ===================== #}
<section class="section pwu-band-green pwu-band-green--tight">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <blockquote class="pwu-quote pwu-quote--light">
      <p>&ldquo;I look forward to writing my check to Full Supply every month because I know it&rsquo;s going to a good cause.&rdquo;</p>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===================== CLOSING CTA ===================== #}
<section class="section pwu-close">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pwu-close__head">
      <h2>Will you partner with us?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pwu-close__steps">
      <div class="pwu-close__step">
        <h3>Consider<br>Prayerfully</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="pwu-close__step">
        <h3>Give<br>Cheerfully</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="pwu-close__step">
        <h3>Join Our<br>Investor Team</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pwu-close__cta">
      {{ button("Donate", paypalUrl, attrs='target="_blank" rel="noopener"') }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script src="{{ '/assets/js/partner-with-us.js' | url }}" defer></script>
